sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_088_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: WebSocket Subprotocol negotiation

    CP->>CS: 1. HTTP Upgrade Request
    Note left of CP: Sec-WebSocket-Protocol: ocpp0.1

    CS--xCP: 2. Central System REJECTS connection
    Note right of CS: Unsupported subprotocol<br/>Connection NOT upgraded

    CP->>CS: 3. HTTP Upgrade Request
    Note left of CP: Sec-WebSocket-Protocol: ocpp0.1,ocpp1.6

    CS-->>CP: 4. Central System ACCEPTS connection
    Note right of CS: Sec-WebSocket-Protocol: ocpp1.6<br/>Connection upgraded to WebSocket

    Note over CP,CS: Validation: Response header must contain<br/>Sec-WebSocket-Protocol: ocpp1.6
